  "title": "ShaderSourceOptions",
  "description": "Construction options for ShaderSource. At least one language must be supplied. Provide `glsl` for WebGL2, `wgsl` for WebGPU, or both for backend-portable materials. The source is compiled lazily on first use against the active backend; an unsupported backend at draw time throws with a clear error.",
